{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I want to share with you"},{"time":2000,"text":"over the next 18 minutes"},{"time":4000,"text":"a pretty incredible idea."},{"time":6000,"text":"Actually, it's a really big idea."},{"time":8000,"text":"But to get us started,"},{"time":10000,"text":"I want to ask if everyone"},{"time":12000,"text":"could just close your eyes for two seconds"},{"time":14000,"text":"and try and think of a technology or a bit of science"},{"time":17000,"text":"that you think has changed the world."},{"time":23000,"text":"Now I bet, in this audience,"},{"time":25000,"text":"you're thinking of some really incredible technology,"},{"time":27000,"text":"some stuff that I haven't even heard of,"},{"time":29000,"text":"I'm absolutely sure."},{"time":31000,"text":"But I'm also sure, pretty sure,"},{"time":34000,"text":"that absolutely nobody is thinking of this."},{"time":38000,"text":"This is a polio vaccine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":41000,"text":"And it's a great thing actually"},{"time":43000,"text":"that nobody's had to think about it here today"},{"time":45000,"text":"because it means that we can take this for granted."},{"time":47000,"text":"This is a great technology."},{"time":49000,"text":"We can take it completely for granted."},{"time":51000,"text":"But it wasn't always that way."},{"time":54000,"text":"Even here in California,"},{"time":57000,"text":"if we were to go back just a few years,"},{"time":59000,"text":"it was a very different story."},{"time":61000,"text":"People were terrified of this disease."},{"time":63000,"text":"They were terrified of polio, and it would cause public panic."},{"time":66000,"text":"And it was because of scenes like this."},{"time":69000,"text":"In this scene,"},{"time":71000,"text":"people are living in an iron lung."},{"time":73000,"text":"These are people who were perfectly healthy two or three days before,"},{"time":76000,"text":"and then two days later,"},{"time":78000,"text":"they can no longer breathe,"},{"time":80000,"text":"and this polio virus has paralyzed"},{"time":82000,"text":"not only their arms and their legs,"},{"time":84000,"text":"but also their breathing muscles."},{"time":86000,"text":"And they were going to spend the rest of their lives, usually,"},{"time":89000,"text":"in this iron lung to breathe for them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91000,"text":"This disease was terrifying."},{"time":93000,"text":"There was no cure,"},{"time":95000,"text":"and there was no vaccine."},{"time":97000,"text":"The disease was so terrifying"},{"time":99000,"text":"that the president of the United States"},{"time":101000,"text":"launched an extraordinary national effort"},{"time":104000,"text":"to find a way to stop it."},{"time":107000,"text":"Twenty years later, they succeeded"},{"time":110000,"text":"and developed the polio vaccine."},{"time":112000,"text":"It was hailed as a scientific miracle"},{"time":114000,"text":"in the late 1950s."},{"time":116000,"text":"Finally, a vaccine that could stop this awful disease,"},{"time":119000,"text":"and here in the United States"},{"time":121000,"text":"it had an incredible impact."},{"time":123000,"text":"As you can see, the virus stopped,"},{"time":125000,"text":"and it stopped very, very fast."}]},{"cues":[{"time":128000,"text":"But this wasn't the case"},{"time":131000,"text":"everywhere in the world."},{"time":133000,"text":"And it happened so fast in the United States, however,"},{"time":136000,"text":"that even just last month Jon Stewart said this:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":139000,"text":"(Video) Jon Stewart: Where is polio still active?"},{"time":141000,"text":"Because I thought that had been eradicated"},{"time":144000,"text":"in the way that smallpox had been eradicated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146000,"text":"Bruce Aylward: Oops. Jon, polio's almost been eradicated."},{"time":150000,"text":"But the reality is"},{"time":152000,"text":"that polio still exists today."},{"time":154000,"text":"We made this map for Jon to try to show him exactly where polio still exists."},{"time":157000,"text":"This is the picture."},{"time":159000,"text":"There's not very much left in the world."},{"time":162000,"text":"But the reason there's not very much left"},{"time":164000,"text":"is because there's been an extraordinary public/private partnership"},{"time":167000,"text":"working behind the scenes, almost unknown,"},{"time":170000,"text":"I'm sure to most of you here today."},{"time":172000,"text":"It's been working for 20 years"},{"time":174000,"text":"to try and eradicate this disease,"},{"time":176000,"text":"and it's got it down to these few cases"},{"time":178000,"text":"that you can see here on this graphic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181000,"text":"But just last year,"},{"time":183000,"text":"we had an incredible shock"},{"time":185000,"text":"and realized that almost just isn't good enough"},{"time":188000,"text":"with a virus like polio."},{"time":191000,"text":"And this is the reason:"},{"time":193000,"text":"in two countries"},{"time":195000,"text":"that hadn't had this disease for more than probably a decade,"},{"time":198000,"text":"on opposite sides of the globe,"},{"time":200000,"text":"there was suddenly terrible polio outbreaks."},{"time":203000,"text":"Hundreds of people were paralyzed."},{"time":205000,"text":"Hundreds of people died --"},{"time":208000,"text":"children as well as adults."},{"time":210000,"text":"And in both cases,"},{"time":212000,"text":"we were able to use genetic sequencing to look at the polio viruses,"},{"time":215000,"text":"and we could tell these viruses were not from these countries."},{"time":218000,"text":"They had come from thousands of miles away."},{"time":221000,"text":"And in one case, it originated on another continent."},{"time":224000,"text":"And not only that, but when they came into these countries,"},{"time":227000,"text":"then they got on commercial jetliners probably"},{"time":230000,"text":"and they traveled even farther"},{"time":232000,"text":"to other places like Russia,"},{"time":234000,"text":"where, for the first time in over a decade last year,"},{"time":237000,"text":"children were crippled and paralyzed"},{"time":240000,"text":"by a disease that they had not seen for years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":244000,"text":"Now all of these outbreaks that I just showed you,"},{"time":247000,"text":"these are under control now,"},{"time":249000,"text":"and it looks like they'll probably stop very, very quickly."},{"time":252000,"text":"But the message was very clear."},{"time":255000,"text":"Polio is still"},{"time":257000,"text":"a devastating, explosive disease."},{"time":260000,"text":"It's just happening in another part of the world."},{"time":264000,"text":"And our big idea"},{"time":267000,"text":"is that the scientific miracle of this decade"},{"time":271000,"text":"should be the complete eradication"},{"time":273000,"text":"of poliomyelitis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":275000,"text":"So I want to tell you a little bit"},{"time":277000,"text":"about what this partnership, the Polio Partnership,"},{"time":279000,"text":"is trying to do."},{"time":281000,"text":"We're not trying to control polio."},{"time":283000,"text":"We're not trying to get it down to just a few cases,"},{"time":286000,"text":"because this disease is like a root fire;"},{"time":288000,"text":"it can explode again if you don't snuff it out completely."},{"time":291000,"text":"So what we're looking for"},{"time":293000,"text":"is a permanent solution."},{"time":295000,"text":"We want a world in which every child, just like you guys,"},{"time":298000,"text":"can take for granted"},{"time":300000,"text":"a polio-free world."},{"time":302000,"text":"So we're looking for a permanent solution,"},{"time":304000,"text":"and this is where we get lucky."},{"time":306000,"text":"This is one of the very few viruses in the world"},{"time":309000,"text":"where there are big enough cracks in its armor"},{"time":311000,"text":"that we can try to do something truly extraordinary."},{"time":314000,"text":"This virus can only survive in people."},{"time":317000,"text":"It can't live for a very long time in people."},{"time":319000,"text":"It doesn't survive in the environment hardly at all."},{"time":322000,"text":"And we've got pretty good vaccines, as I've just showed you."},{"time":325000,"text":"So we are trying"},{"time":327000,"text":"to wipe out this virus completely."},{"time":330000,"text":"What the polio eradication program is trying to do"},{"time":333000,"text":"is to kill the virus itself"},{"time":335000,"text":"that causes polio"},{"time":337000,"text":"everywhere on Earth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":339000,"text":"Now we don't have a great track record"},{"time":341000,"text":"when it comes to doing something like this,"},{"time":343000,"text":"to eradicating diseases."},{"time":345000,"text":"It's been tried six times in the last century,"},{"time":348000,"text":"and it's been successful exactly once."},{"time":352000,"text":"And this is because disease eradication,"},{"time":355000,"text":"it's still the venture capital of public health."},{"time":358000,"text":"The risks are massive,"},{"time":360000,"text":"but the pay-off --"},{"time":363000,"text":"economic, humanitarian, motivational --"},{"time":365000,"text":"it's absolutely huge."},{"time":367000,"text":"One congressman here in the United States"},{"time":370000,"text":"thinks that the entire investment"},{"time":373000,"text":"that the U.S. put into smallpox eradication"},{"time":375000,"text":"pays itself off every 26 days --"},{"time":378000,"text":"in foregone treatment costs"},{"time":380000,"text":"and vaccination costs."},{"time":382000,"text":"And if we can finish polio eradication,"},{"time":385000,"text":"the poorest countries in the world"},{"time":387000,"text":"are going to save over 50 billion dollars"},{"time":391000,"text":"in the next 25 years alone."},{"time":394000,"text":"So those are the kind of stakes that we're after."}]},{"cues":[{"time":397000,"text":"But smallpox eradication was hard;"},{"time":399000,"text":"it was very, very hard."},{"time":401000,"text":"And polio eradication, in many ways, is even tougher,"},{"time":404000,"text":"and there's a few reasons for that."},{"time":407000,"text":"The first is that,"},{"time":409000,"text":"when we started trying to eradicate polio"},{"time":411000,"text":"about 20 years ago,"},{"time":413000,"text":"more than twice as many countries were infected"},{"time":415000,"text":"than had been when we started off with smallpox."},{"time":418000,"text":"And there were more than 10 times as many people"},{"time":420000,"text":"living in these countries."},{"time":422000,"text":"So it was a massive effort."},{"time":424000,"text":"The second challenge we had was --"},{"time":426000,"text":"in contrast to the smallpox vaccine,"},{"time":428000,"text":"which was very stable, and a single dose protected you for life --"},{"time":431000,"text":"the polio vaccine is incredibly fragile."},{"time":434000,"text":"It deteriorates so quickly in the tropics"},{"time":437000,"text":"that we've had to put this special vaccine monitor"},{"time":439000,"text":"on every single vial"},{"time":441000,"text":"so that it will change very quickly"},{"time":443000,"text":"when it's exposed to too much heat,"},{"time":445000,"text":"and we can tell that it's not a good vaccine to use on a child --"},{"time":448000,"text":"it's not potent; it's not going to protect them."},{"time":450000,"text":"Even then, kids need many doses of the vaccine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":453000,"text":"But the third challenge we have --"},{"time":455000,"text":"and probably even bigger one, the biggest challenge --"},{"time":458000,"text":"is that, in contrast to smallpox where you could always see your enemy --"},{"time":461000,"text":"every single person almost who was infected with smallpox"},{"time":464000,"text":"had this telltale rash."},{"time":466000,"text":"So you could get around the disease;"},{"time":468000,"text":"you could vaccinate around the disease and cut it off."},{"time":471000,"text":"With polio it's almost completely different."},{"time":474000,"text":"The vast majority of people who are infected with the polio virus"},{"time":477000,"text":"show absolutely no sign of the disease."},{"time":480000,"text":"So you can't see the enemy most of the time,"},{"time":483000,"text":"and as a result,"},{"time":485000,"text":"we've needed a very different approach to eradicate polio"},{"time":488000,"text":"than what was done with smallpox."}]},{"cues":[{"time":490000,"text":"We've had to create"},{"time":492000,"text":"one of the largest social movements in history."},{"time":495000,"text":"There's over 10 million people,"},{"time":497000,"text":"probably 20 million people,"},{"time":499000,"text":"largely volunteers,"},{"time":501000,"text":"who have been working over the last 20 years"},{"time":503000,"text":"in what has now been called"},{"time":505000,"text":"the largest internationally-coordinated operation in peacetime."},{"time":509000,"text":"These people, these 20 million people,"},{"time":512000,"text":"vaccinate over 500 million children"},{"time":515000,"text":"every single year,"},{"time":517000,"text":"multiple times"},{"time":519000,"text":"at the peak of our operation."},{"time":522000,"text":"Now giving the polio vaccine is simple."},{"time":524000,"text":"It's just two drops, like that."},{"time":526000,"text":"But reaching 500 million people"},{"time":528000,"text":"is much, much tougher."},{"time":530000,"text":"And these vaccinators, these volunteers,"},{"time":533000,"text":"they have got to dive headlong"},{"time":535000,"text":"into some of the toughest, densest"},{"time":537000,"text":"urban slums in the world."},{"time":539000,"text":"They've got to trek under sweltering suns"},{"time":542000,"text":"to some of the most remote, difficult to reach places in the world."},{"time":546000,"text":"And they also have to dodge bullets,"},{"time":548000,"text":"because we have got to operate"},{"time":550000,"text":"during shaky cease-fires and truces"},{"time":552000,"text":"to try and vaccinate children,"},{"time":554000,"text":"even in areas affected by conflict."}]},{"cues":[{"time":557000,"text":"One reporter"},{"time":559000,"text":"who was watching our program in Somalia about five years ago --"},{"time":562000,"text":"a place which has eradicated polio,"},{"time":564000,"text":"not once, but twice, because they got reinfected."},{"time":566000,"text":"He was sitting outside of the road,"},{"time":568000,"text":"watching one of these polio campaigns unfold,"},{"time":570000,"text":"and a few months later he wrote:"},{"time":572000,"text":"\"This is foreign aid at its most heroic.\""},{"time":576000,"text":"And these heroes, they come from every walk of life,"},{"time":578000,"text":"all sorts of backgrounds."},{"time":580000,"text":"But one of the most extraordinary is Rotary International."},{"time":583000,"text":"This is a group"},{"time":585000,"text":"whose million-strong army of volunteers"},{"time":587000,"text":"have been working to eradicate polio"},{"time":589000,"text":"for over 20 years."},{"time":591000,"text":"They're right at the center of the whole thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":594000,"text":"Now it took years to build up the infrastructure"},{"time":596000,"text":"for polio eradication --"},{"time":598000,"text":"more than 15 years, much longer than it should have --"},{"time":601000,"text":"but once it was built, the results were striking."},{"time":604000,"text":"Within a couple of years,"},{"time":606000,"text":"every country that started polio eradication"},{"time":608000,"text":"rapidly eradicated all three of their polio viruses,"},{"time":612000,"text":"with the exception of four countries that you see here."},{"time":615000,"text":"And in each of those, it was only part of the country."},{"time":619000,"text":"And then, by 1999,"},{"time":621000,"text":"one of the three polio viruses"},{"time":623000,"text":"that we were trying to eradicate"},{"time":625000,"text":"had been completely eradicated worldwide --"},{"time":628000,"text":"proof of concept."},{"time":630000,"text":"And then today,"},{"time":633000,"text":"there's been a 99 percent reduction --"},{"time":635000,"text":"greater than 99 percent reduction --"},{"time":637000,"text":"in the number of children"},{"time":639000,"text":"who are being paralyzed by this awful disease."},{"time":642000,"text":"When we started, over 20 years ago,"},{"time":644000,"text":"1,000 children were being paralyzed"},{"time":646000,"text":"every single day by this virus."},{"time":649000,"text":"Last year, it was 1,000."}]},{"cues":[{"time":652000,"text":"And at the same time,"},{"time":654000,"text":"the polio eradication program"},{"time":656000,"text":"has been working to help with a lot of other areas."},{"time":658000,"text":"It's been working to help control pandemic flu,"},{"time":661000,"text":"SARS for example."},{"time":663000,"text":"It's also tried to save children by doing other things --"},{"time":666000,"text":"giving vitamin A drops, giving measles shots,"},{"time":669000,"text":"giving bed nets against malaria even"},{"time":671000,"text":"during some of these campaigns."},{"time":673000,"text":"But the most exciting thing"},{"time":675000,"text":"that the polio eradication program has been doing"},{"time":677000,"text":"has been to force us,"},{"time":679000,"text":"the international community,"},{"time":681000,"text":"to reach every single child, every single community,"},{"time":684000,"text":"the most vulnerable people in the world,"},{"time":687000,"text":"with the most basic of health services,"},{"time":689000,"text":"irrespective of geography, poverty,"},{"time":693000,"text":"culture and even conflict."}]},{"cues":[{"time":695000,"text":"So things were looking very exciting,"},{"time":697000,"text":"and then about five years ago,"},{"time":699000,"text":"this virus, this ancient virus, started to fight back."},{"time":702000,"text":"The first problem we ran into"},{"time":705000,"text":"was that, in these last four countries, the strongholds of this virus,"},{"time":708000,"text":"we just couldn't seem to get the virus rooted out."},{"time":712000,"text":"And then to make the matters even worse,"},{"time":714000,"text":"the virus started to spread out of these four places,"},{"time":717000,"text":"especially northern India and northern Nigeria,"},{"time":720000,"text":"into much of Africa, Asia, and even into Europe,"},{"time":723000,"text":"causing horrific outbreaks"},{"time":725000,"text":"in places that had not seen this disease for decades."},{"time":729000,"text":"And then,"},{"time":731000,"text":"in one of the most important, tenacious"},{"time":734000,"text":"and toughest reservoirs of the polio virus in the world,"},{"time":737000,"text":"we found that our vaccine was working"},{"time":740000,"text":"half as well as it should have."},{"time":742000,"text":"In conditions like this,"},{"time":744000,"text":"the vaccine just couldn't get the grip it needed to"},{"time":746000,"text":"in the guts of these children"},{"time":748000,"text":"and protect them the way that it needed to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":750000,"text":"Now at that time,"},{"time":752000,"text":"there was a great, as you can imagine,"},{"time":754000,"text":"frustration -- let's call it frustration --"},{"time":756000,"text":"it started to grow very, very quickly."},{"time":758000,"text":"And all of a sudden, some very important voices"},{"time":760000,"text":"in the world of public health"},{"time":762000,"text":"started to say, \"Hang on."},{"time":764000,"text":"We should abandon this idea of eradication."},{"time":767000,"text":"Let's settle for control -- that's good enough.\""},{"time":770000,"text":"Now as seductive as the idea of control sounds,"},{"time":774000,"text":"it's a false premise."},{"time":776000,"text":"The brutal truth is,"},{"time":778000,"text":"if we don't have the will or the skill,"},{"time":780000,"text":"or even the money that we need"},{"time":783000,"text":"to reach children, the most vulnerable children in the world,"},{"time":786000,"text":"with something as simple"},{"time":788000,"text":"as an oral polio vaccine,"},{"time":791000,"text":"then pretty soon,"},{"time":793000,"text":"more than 200,000 children"},{"time":795000,"text":"are again going to be paralyzed by this disease"},{"time":797000,"text":"every single year."},{"time":799000,"text":"There's absolutely no question."}]},{"cues":[{"time":801000,"text":"These are children like Umar."},{"time":804000,"text":"Umar is seven years old,"},{"time":807000,"text":"and he's from northern Nigeria."},{"time":809000,"text":"He lives in a family home there"},{"time":811000,"text":"with his eight brothers and sisters."},{"time":813000,"text":"Umar also has polio."},{"time":816000,"text":"Umar was paralyzed for life."},{"time":818000,"text":"His right leg was paralyzed"},{"time":820000,"text":"in 2004."},{"time":822000,"text":"This leg, his right leg,"},{"time":825000,"text":"now takes an awful beating"},{"time":827000,"text":"because he has to half-crawl,"},{"time":829000,"text":"because it's faster to move that way"},{"time":831000,"text":"to keep up with his friends, keep up with his brothers and sisters,"},{"time":833000,"text":"than to get up on his crutches and walk."},{"time":836000,"text":"But Umar is a fantastic student. He's an incredible kid."},{"time":839000,"text":"As you probably can't see the detail here,"},{"time":841000,"text":"but this is his report card,"},{"time":843000,"text":"and you'll see, he's got perfect scores."},{"time":845000,"text":"He got 100 percent in all the important things,"},{"time":847000,"text":"like nursery rhymes, for example there."},{"time":850000,"text":"But you know I'd love to be able to tell you"},{"time":853000,"text":"that Umar is a typical kid with polio these days,"},{"time":855000,"text":"but it's not true."},{"time":857000,"text":"Umar is an exceptional kid"},{"time":859000,"text":"in exceptional circumstances."}]},{"cues":[{"time":861000,"text":"The reality of polio today"},{"time":863000,"text":"is something very different."},{"time":866000,"text":"Polio strikes the poorest communities in the world."},{"time":870000,"text":"It leaves their children paralyzed,"},{"time":872000,"text":"and it drags their families"},{"time":874000,"text":"deeper into poverty,"},{"time":876000,"text":"because they're desperately searching"},{"time":878000,"text":"and they're desperately spending the little bit of savings that they have,"},{"time":880000,"text":"trying in vain"},{"time":882000,"text":"to find a cure for their children."},{"time":886000,"text":"We think children deserve better."},{"time":889000,"text":"And so when the going got really tough"},{"time":892000,"text":"in the polio eradication program"},{"time":894000,"text":"about two years ago,"},{"time":896000,"text":"when people were saying, \"We should call it off,\""},{"time":898000,"text":"the Polio Partnership"},{"time":900000,"text":"decided to buckle down once again"},{"time":902000,"text":"and try and find innovative new solutions,"},{"time":905000,"text":"new ways to get to the children"},{"time":907000,"text":"that we were missing again and again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":909000,"text":"In northern India, we started mapping the cases"},{"time":911000,"text":"using satellite imaging like this,"},{"time":913000,"text":"so that we could guide our investments and vaccinator shelters,"},{"time":916000,"text":"so we could get to the millions of children"},{"time":918000,"text":"on the Koshi River basin"},{"time":920000,"text":"where there are no other health services."},{"time":922000,"text":"In northern Nigeria,"},{"time":924000,"text":"the political leaders and the traditional Muslim leaders,"},{"time":926000,"text":"they got directly involved in the program"},{"time":928000,"text":"to help solve the problems of logistics"},{"time":930000,"text":"and community confidence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":932000,"text":"And now they've even started using these devices --"},{"time":935000,"text":"speaking of cool technology --"},{"time":937000,"text":"these little devices, little GIS trackers like this,"},{"time":940000,"text":"which they put into the vaccine carriers of their vaccinators."},{"time":943000,"text":"And then they can track them,"},{"time":945000,"text":"and at the end of the day, they look and see,"},{"time":947000,"text":"did these guys get every single street, every single house."},{"time":949000,"text":"This is the kind of commitment now we're seeing"},{"time":952000,"text":"to try and reach all of the children we've been missing."},{"time":955000,"text":"And in Afghanistan, we're trying new approaches --"},{"time":958000,"text":"access negotiators."},{"time":960000,"text":"We're working closely with the International Committee of the Red Cross"},{"time":963000,"text":"to ensure that we can reach every child."}]},{"cues":[{"time":966000,"text":"But as we tried these extraordinary things,"},{"time":969000,"text":"as people went to this trouble"},{"time":971000,"text":"to try and rework their tactics,"},{"time":973000,"text":"we went back to the vaccine -- it's a 50-year-old vaccine --"},{"time":976000,"text":"and we thought, surely we can make a better vaccine,"},{"time":979000,"text":"so that when they finally get to these kids,"},{"time":981000,"text":"we can have a better bang for our buck."},{"time":983000,"text":"And this started an incredible collaboration with industry,"},{"time":986000,"text":"and within six months,"},{"time":988000,"text":"we were testing a new polio vaccine"},{"time":990000,"text":"that targeted, just two years ago,"},{"time":992000,"text":"the last two types of polio in the world."},{"time":995000,"text":"Now June the ninth, 2009,"},{"time":998000,"text":"we got the first results from the first trial with this vaccine,"},{"time":1001000,"text":"and it turned out to be a game-changer."},{"time":1003000,"text":"The new vaccine"},{"time":1005000,"text":"had twice the impact on these last couple of viruses"},{"time":1008000,"text":"as the old vaccine had,"},{"time":1010000,"text":"and we immediately started using this."},{"time":1012000,"text":"Well, in a couple of months we had to get it out of production."},{"time":1015000,"text":"And it started rolling off the production lines"},{"time":1017000,"text":"and into the mouths of children around the world."},{"time":1019000,"text":"And we didn't start with the easy places."},{"time":1021000,"text":"The first place this vaccine was used"},{"time":1023000,"text":"was in southern Afghanistan,"},{"time":1025000,"text":"because it's in places like that"},{"time":1027000,"text":"where kids are going to benefit the most"},{"time":1029000,"text":"from technologies like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1031000,"text":"Now here at TED, over the last couple of days,"},{"time":1034000,"text":"I've seen people challenging the audience again and again"},{"time":1038000,"text":"to believe in the impossible."},{"time":1041000,"text":"So this morning at about seven o'clock,"},{"time":1044000,"text":"I decided that we'd try to drive Chris"},{"time":1046000,"text":"and the production crew here berserk"},{"time":1048000,"text":"by downloading all of our data from India again,"},{"time":1052000,"text":"so that you could see something"},{"time":1054000,"text":"that's just unfolding today,"},{"time":1056000,"text":"which proves that the impossible is possible."},{"time":1060000,"text":"And only two years ago, people were saying that this is impossible."},{"time":1063000,"text":"Now remember, northern India is the perfect storm"},{"time":1066000,"text":"when it comes to polio."},{"time":1068000,"text":"Over 500,000 children"},{"time":1070000,"text":"are born in the two states that have never stopped polio --"},{"time":1073000,"text":"Uttar Pradesh and Bihar --"},{"time":1076000,"text":"500,000 children every single month."},{"time":1078000,"text":"Sanitation is terrible,"},{"time":1080000,"text":"and our old vaccine, you remember,"},{"time":1082000,"text":"worked half as well as it should have."},{"time":1085000,"text":"And yet, the impossible is happening."},{"time":1088000,"text":"Today marks exactly six months --"},{"time":1092000,"text":"and for the first time in history,"},{"time":1094000,"text":"not a single child has been paralyzed"},{"time":1096000,"text":"in Uttar Pradesh or Bihar."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1098000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1109000,"text":"India's not unique."},{"time":1112000,"text":"In Umar's home country of Nigeria,"},{"time":1114000,"text":"a 95 percent reduction"},{"time":1116000,"text":"in the number of children paralyzed by polio last year."},{"time":1119000,"text":"And in the last six months,"},{"time":1121000,"text":"we've had less places reinfected by polio"},{"time":1123000,"text":"than at any other time in history."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1127000,"text":"Ladies and gentlemen, with a combination"},{"time":1129000,"text":"of smart people, smart technology"},{"time":1131000,"text":"and smart investments,"},{"time":1133000,"text":"polio can now be eradicated anywhere."},{"time":1137000,"text":"We have major challenges, you can imagine,"},{"time":1139000,"text":"to finish this job,"},{"time":1141000,"text":"but as you've also seen,"},{"time":1143000,"text":"it's doable,"},{"time":1145000,"text":"it has great secondary benefits,"},{"time":1147000,"text":"and polio eradication is a great buy."},{"time":1150000,"text":"And as long as any child anywhere"},{"time":1153000,"text":"is paralyzed by this virus,"},{"time":1155000,"text":"it's a stark reminder"},{"time":1157000,"text":"that we are failing, as a society, to reach children"},{"time":1160000,"text":"with the most basic of services."},{"time":1162000,"text":"And for that reason, polio eradication:"},{"time":1164000,"text":"it's the ultimate in equity"},{"time":1167000,"text":"and it's the ultimate in social justice."},{"time":1170000,"text":"The huge social movement"},{"time":1172000,"text":"that's been involved in polio eradication"},{"time":1174000,"text":"is ready to do way more for these children."},{"time":1176000,"text":"It's ready to reach them with bed nets, with other things."},{"time":1179000,"text":"But capitalizing on their enthusiasm,"},{"time":1182000,"text":"capitalizing on their energy"},{"time":1184000,"text":"means finishing the job"},{"time":1186000,"text":"that they started 20 years ago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1189000,"text":"Finishing polio is a smart thing to do,"},{"time":1192000,"text":"and it's the right thing to do."},{"time":1194000,"text":"Now we're in tough times economically."},{"time":1197000,"text":"But as David Cameron of the United Kingdom"},{"time":1200000,"text":"said about a month ago when he was talking about polio,"},{"time":1203000,"text":"\"There's never a wrong time"},{"time":1205000,"text":"to do the right thing.\""},{"time":1207000,"text":"Finishing polio eradication"},{"time":1209000,"text":"is the right thing to do."},{"time":1211000,"text":"And we are at a crossroads right now"},{"time":1213000,"text":"in this great effort over the last 20 years."},{"time":1215000,"text":"We have a new vaccine,"},{"time":1217000,"text":"we have new resolve,"},{"time":1219000,"text":"and we have new tactics."},{"time":1221000,"text":"We have the chance"},{"time":1223000,"text":"to write an entirely new polio-free chapter"},{"time":1226000,"text":"in human history."},{"time":1229000,"text":"But if we blink now,"},{"time":1232000,"text":"we will lose forever"},{"time":1234000,"text":"the chance to eradicate an ancient disease."},{"time":1239000,"text":"Here's a great idea to spread:"},{"time":1242000,"text":"End polio now."},{"time":1244000,"text":"Help us tell the story."},{"time":1246000,"text":"Help us build the momentum"},{"time":1248000,"text":"so that very soon"},{"time":1250000,"text":"every child, every parent"},{"time":1252000,"text":"everywhere"},{"time":1254000,"text":"can also take for granted"},{"time":1256000,"text":"a polio-free life forever."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1259000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1261000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1283000,"text":"Bill Gates: Well Bruce, where do you think the toughest places are going to be?"},{"time":1286000,"text":"Where would you say we need to be the smartest?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1289000,"text":"BA: The four places where you saw, that we've never stopped --"},{"time":1292000,"text":"northern Nigeria, northern India,"},{"time":1294000,"text":"the southern corner of Afghanistan"},{"time":1296000,"text":"and bordering areas of Pakistan --"},{"time":1298000,"text":"they're going to be the toughest."},{"time":1300000,"text":"But the interesting thing is, of those three,"},{"time":1302000,"text":"India's looking real good, as you just saw in the data."},{"time":1304000,"text":"And Afghanistan, Afghanistan, we think"},{"time":1306000,"text":"has probably stopped polio repeatedly."},{"time":1308000,"text":"It keeps getting reinfected."},{"time":1310000,"text":"So the tough ones: going to get the top of Nigeria finished"},{"time":1312000,"text":"and getting Pakistan finished."},{"time":1314000,"text":"They're going to be the tough ones."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1316000,"text":"BG: Now what about the money?"},{"time":1318000,"text":"Give us a sense of how much the campaign costs a year."},{"time":1321000,"text":"And is it easy to raise that money?"},{"time":1324000,"text":"And what's it going to be like the next couple of years?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1326000,"text":"BA: It's interesting."},{"time":1328000,"text":"We spend right now about 750 million"},{"time":1330000,"text":"to 800 million dollars a year."},{"time":1333000,"text":"That's what it costs to reach 500 million children."},{"time":1335000,"text":"It sounds like a lot of money; it is a lot of money."},{"time":1338000,"text":"But when you're reaching 500 million children multiple times --"},{"time":1341000,"text":"20, 30 cents to reach a child --"},{"time":1343000,"text":"that's not very much money."},{"time":1345000,"text":"But right now we don't have enough of that."},{"time":1347000,"text":"We have a big gap in that money. We're cutting corners,"},{"time":1349000,"text":"and every time we cut corners,"},{"time":1351000,"text":"more places get infected that shouldn't have, and it just slows us down."},{"time":1354000,"text":"And that great buy costs us a little bit more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1357000,"text":"BG: Well, hopefully we'll get the word out,"},{"time":1360000,"text":"and the governments will keep their generosity up."},{"time":1363000,"text":"So good luck. We're all in this with you."},{"time":1365000,"text":"Thank you. (BA: Thank you.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1367000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}